item.title: Skateboard
item.description: In the Summer of 2025, during my internship at ATI motors, I built a prototype of an intelligent fork for pallet transportation. “Skateboard” is a nickname given to the project.

item.title: Mailbox matching game
item.description: As a part of Purdue EPICS, a service-led engineering projection, my team and I built a mailbox matching game for the riders at Agape therapeutic riding.
